sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as DSP API Server
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>Metrics: 9090/TCP<br/>Healthz: 6060/TCP
    participant ArgoExec as argoexec<br/>(Init/Sidecar)
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>443/TCP or 9000/TCP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over DSP,PG: Flow 1: Workflow Execution (DSP Pipeline Run)

    DSP->>K8s: 1. Submit Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8s-->>WFC: 2. Watch notification<br/>HTTPS, SA Token
    WFC->>K8s: 3. Create Pod for step<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Note over ArgoExec: Pod starts with argoexec<br/>init container
    ArgoExec->>K8s: 4. Get Workflow spec<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Note over ArgoExec: Execute step logic
    ArgoExec->>S3: 5. Upload artifacts<br/>HTTPS or HTTP<br/>Access Key/Secret Key
    S3-->>ArgoExec: Artifact stored
    ArgoExec->>K8s: 6. Patch Pod annotations<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8s-->>WFC: Step completion notification
    WFC->>K8s: Schedule next DAG step(s)

    Note over WFC,PG: Flow 2: Workflow Archival (Optional)

    WFC->>PG: Archive workflow state<br/>TCP/5432, TLS configurable<br/>Username/Password

    Note over Prom,WFC: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prom->>WFC: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/9090, plaintext<br/>No auth
    WFC-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
